’Ł@c2824c34ee3f9fc2bd2e7c450200f0baeef50f1497500d9c6904da86af24e0beŁøTitle: title: into value
Path: Notes
Content:
Custom values from plugins have a base value representation. This extracts that base value representation. For streams use 
``collect``
.
